{"title":"森林之花","authors":["傅仇"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":12,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林之花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傅仇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云崖上有位少女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"森林里流送木材的“洪道”，衔接大江激流。“洪道”口的崖上，立着工棚，有女工守护。她像通讯兵一样，和山上流送工人取得紧密联系，保证安全放送木材，使山上木材有次序地奔进大江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洪波滚滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"波涛拥挤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂浪拍击云崖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野马不敢停蹄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云崖上有个工棚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工棚里有个少女。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪花飞在头上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水珠溅上花衣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不捏把冷汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云崖别崩落江底！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她才满面春风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像大树站在那里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她背靠青山绿林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼光射在激流里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她手摇电话机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向流送工人飞报消息："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“水路畅通无阻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓紧大好时机。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千山木材变成龙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘风破浪飞千里！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消息飞传高山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林谷回声四起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木材滚滚飞来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声音猛如雷雨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万筒木材奔大江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万株水柱破云起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个声音在高呼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再见！亲爱的少女！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫天水柱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫天花雨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画出一条彩虹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起坚强的少女！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪里送炭的小伙子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明。严寒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧张的高原车站。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒸汽腾空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟雾迷漫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一夜大雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冻结了百辆汽车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝色的车辆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成了座座雪堆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个伶俐的小伙子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头戴雪帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身披蓝衣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提着一盆火炭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在烟雾里钻来钻去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东边的司机在呐喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子在东边出现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西边的司机在呼叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子又出现在西边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子雪里送炭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上冒着热汗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子就像一团火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪地上红光闪闪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽车挨着小伙子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全身解冻叫得欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"司机挨着小伙子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手脚灵活心温暖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喇叭声声高叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽车开出车站。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车头上伸出百只手掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向小伙子送出深情的语言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车队已飞越高山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子还站在车站门前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双秀丽的大眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道出了千万句平安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽车已经远行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子还在打扫车站。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是小伙子的名声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已飞遍雪山高原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日出，烟消雾散，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子脸上红光闪闪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀！原来是个美丽的姑娘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一身光彩照亮了车站。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}